-- Jordan Plans to Offer Oil Exploration Tender, Al Ghad Reports
-- B y   M o h a m m a d   T a y s e e r
-- 2012-01-03T10:03:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-03/jordan-plans-to-offer-oil-exploration-tender-al-ghad-reports.html
Jordan plans to offer an oil
exploration tender this month, Al Ghad said, citing the director
general of the National Resources Authority.  International companies can bid for the project to help
identify “promising” areas to drill for oil in the kingdom,
Mousa Ali Alzyoud said in the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mohammad Tayseer through the Dubai newsroom at 
